1
00:00:02,000 --> 00:00:03,710
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

2
00:00:04,299 --> 00:00:05,985
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Unfortunately
there's a good chance</b></Default>

3
00:00:06,009 --> 00:00:08,655
<Default><b>the Emperor Dragon has
taken over Gaelion's mind.</b></Default>

4
00:00:08,679 --> 00:00:10,439
<Default><b>What do you
mean by that?</b></Default>

5
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:13,179
<Default><b>To put simply</b></Default>

6
00:00:13,259 --> 00:00:14,655
<Default><b>that contains
their mind.</b></Default>

7
00:00:14,679 --> 00:00:17,940
<Default><b>You're able to use that core
to improve your abilities</b></Default>

8
00:00:18,019 --> 00:00:20,940
<Default><b>or even inherit the memories
that reside in the dragon.</b></Default>

9
00:00:21,149 --> 00:00:23,190
<Default><b>Oh, so basically</b></Default>

10
00:00:23,269 --> 00:00:24,666
<Default><b>the dragon zombie's mind</b></Default>

11
00:00:24,690 --> 00:00:26,890
<Default><b>absorbed
by the Emperor Dragon's core</b></Default>

12
00:00:26,989 --> 00:00:29,660
<Default><b>caused Gaelion to
lose control of himself.</b></Default>

13
00:00:30,109 --> 00:00:31,296
<Default><b>[SADEENA] Yes.</b></Default>

14
00:00:31,320 --> 00:00:33,869
<Default><b>No way. It's
like I thought.</b></Default>

15
00:00:34,950 --> 00:00:38,039
<Default><b>Hey, Ake, the old lady
and Rishia are out right now.</b></Default>

16
00:00:38,119 --> 00:00:39,265
<Default><b>Bring 'em back here!</b></Default>

17
00:00:39,289 --> 00:00:40,289
<Default><b>On it.</b></Default>

18
00:00:40,329 --> 00:00:44,170
<Default><b>Rat, I want you to protect
the village in our absence.</b></Default>

19
00:00:44,340 --> 00:00:46,566
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I'll send S'yne too
if you need her.</b></Default>

20
00:00:46,590 --> 00:00:49,066
<Default><b>Keep an eye on the monsters
till we're back.</b></Default>

21
00:00:49,090 --> 00:00:50,730
<Default><b>Right. Leave it to me.</b></Default>

22
00:00:50,890 --> 00:00:52,316
<Default><b>I'll go after Gaelion</b></Default>

23
00:00:52,340 --> 00:00:55,509
<Default><b>along with Raphtlaia</b></Default>

24
00:00:55,770 --> 00:00:57,020
<Default><b>Sir Naofumi!</b></Default>

25
00:00:58,020 --> 00:00:59,576
<Default><b>[ECLAIR] I need you to
come with me.</b></Default>

26
00:00:59,600 --> 00:01:01,600
<Default><b>Filo suddenly collapsed
in pain.</b></Default>

27
00:01:02,020 --> 00:01:03,625
<Default><b>- [NAOFUMI] Filo?
- The healers are doing</b></Default>

28
00:01:03,649 --> 00:01:04,835
<Default><b>everything they can</b></Default>

29
00:01:04,859 --> 00:01:06,295
<Default><b>but it's not helping.</b></Default>

30
00:01:06,319 --> 00:01:07,585
<Default><b>Master Naofumi.</b></Default>

31
00:01:07,609 --> 00:01:10,450
<Default><b>Raphtalia and I will
go ahead and check on Filo.</b></Default>

32
00:01:10,859 --> 00:01:13,596
<Default><b>The rest of you should
prepare to go while we're gone.</b></Default>

33
00:01:13,620 --> 00:01:14,715
<Default><b>Understood.</b></Default>

34
00:01:14,739 --> 00:01:16,516
<Default><b>Allow me to
come with you.</b></Default>

35
00:01:16,540 --> 00:01:19,000
<Default><b>I feel like I maybe able to
help somehow.</b></Default>

36
00:01:19,250 --> 00:01:20,490
<Default><b>I'll go too!</b></Default>

37
00:01:20,540 --> 00:01:21,750
<Default><b>Me too!</b></Default>

38
00:01:21,829 --> 00:01:24,290
<Default><b>I'm too worried about Filo
to stay!</b></Default>

39
00:01:24,750 --> 00:01:26,170
<Default><b>Hm.</b></Default>

40
00:01:32,680 --> 00:01:34,219
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

41
00:01:35,219 --> 00:01:36,719
<Default><b>Let's get going.</b></Default>

42
00:03:07,689 --> 00:03:09,150
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

43
00:03:10,900 --> 00:03:12,400
<Default><b>Naofumi, quick!</b></Default>

44
00:03:12,479 --> 00:03:13,716
<Default><b>Where's Filo?</b></Default>

45
00:03:13,740 --> 00:03:15,300
<Default><b>This way! But hurry!</b></Default>

46
00:03:15,650 --> 00:03:17,360
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

47
00:03:17,909 --> 00:03:19,869
<Default><b>- Are you okay?
- Are you okay?</b></Default>

48
00:03:21,490 --> 00:03:22,909
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

49
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:24,720
<Default><b>Master, you came for me.</b></Default>

50
00:03:24,750 --> 00:03:25,919
<Default><b>Thank you.</b></Default>

51
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:28,879
<Default><b>Don't you worry.
I'll fix you up right away</b></Default>

52
00:03:29,379 --> 00:03:31,500
<Default><b>Master
Naofumi, this is...</b></Default>

53
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:34,650
<Default><b>It's worse than
what the Curse Series did.</b></Default>

54
00:03:40,219 --> 00:03:41,786
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Her levels are dropping?</b></Default>

55
00:03:41,810 --> 00:03:43,075
<Default><b>What's going on?</b></Default>

56
00:03:43,099 --> 00:03:44,955
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] It's too odd to be
a coincidence</b></Default>

57
00:03:44,979 --> 00:03:47,419
<Default><b>could Gaelion have
something to do with it.</b></Default>

58
00:03:50,110 --> 00:03:52,229
<Default><b>I'm able to sense
a terrible power</b></Default>

59
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:54,239
<Default><b>flowing out
from within Filo.</b></Default>

60
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:55,819
<Default><b>Could it be</b></Default>

61
00:03:55,900 --> 00:03:59,006
<Default><b>that her experience points are
being transferred to Gaelion?</b></Default>

62
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:00,280
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

63
00:04:00,490 --> 00:04:01,596
<Default><b>Hang in there!</b></Default>

64
00:04:01,620 --> 00:04:02,789
<Default><b>Oh.</b></Default>

65
00:04:02,949 --> 00:04:05,250
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Master Naofumi</b></Default>

66
00:04:10,039 --> 00:04:11,289
<Default><b>Atla?</b></Default>

67
00:04:11,539 --> 00:04:14,090
<Default><b>[ATLA] I'll try to dampen
the flow of power.</b></Default>

68
00:04:20,009 --> 00:04:22,509
<Default><b>Ah. That's strange.</b></Default>

69
00:04:22,600 --> 00:04:25,156
<Default><b>[FILO] For some reason
I feel a little bit better now.</b></Default>

70
00:04:25,180 --> 00:04:26,365
<Default><b>Thank goodness!</b></Default>

71
00:04:26,389 --> 00:04:27,389
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

72
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:28,665
<Default><b>That's a relief!</b></Default>

73
00:04:28,689 --> 00:04:29,769
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

74
00:04:31,189 --> 00:04:33,086
<Default><b>It's not much but I think
this should buy you</b></Default>

75
00:04:33,110 --> 00:04:34,125
<Default><b>a little more time.</b></Default>

76
00:04:34,149 --> 00:04:35,429
<Default><b>Thanks, Atla.</b></Default>

77
00:04:36,779 --> 00:04:38,045
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Even at this slower speed</b></Default>

78
00:04:38,069 --> 00:04:39,755
<Default><b>she won't last two days.</b></Default>

79
00:04:39,779 --> 00:04:41,425
<Default><b>She'll drop
to level one.</b></Default>

80
00:04:41,449 --> 00:04:43,699
<Default><b>No, we'll be lucky
if it stops there.</b></Default>

81
00:04:44,410 --> 00:04:47,079
<Default><b>At this rate</b></Default>

82
00:04:51,670 --> 00:04:52,726
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
I want you to stay here</b></Default>

83
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:53,855
<Default><b>and take care of Filo.</b></Default>

84
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:55,050
<Default><b>[gasping]</b></Default>

85
00:04:55,500 --> 00:04:58,220
<Default><b>I'm going to break the curse
that was laid on her.</b></Default>

86
00:04:58,629 --> 00:05:00,189
<Default><b>Let's go, Raphtalia.</b></Default>

87
00:05:00,220 --> 00:05:01,470
<Default><b>[FILO] No!</b></Default>

88
00:05:01,550 --> 00:05:03,970
<Default><b>Please don't
leave me here</b></Default>

89
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:06,196
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] You need to stay here
and rest.</b></Default>

90
00:05:06,220 --> 00:05:07,365
<Default><b>But if I stay here</b></Default>

91
00:05:07,389 --> 00:05:09,706
<Default><b>then who's going to
pull your carriage, Master!</b></Default>

92
00:05:09,730 --> 00:05:11,536
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Enough.
You're not in any shape to do...</b></Default>

93
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:14,040
<Default><b>Well, if Filo's going with you
then so am I!</b></Default>

94
00:05:14,269 --> 00:05:15,915
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Melty, you're a princess!</b></Default>

95
00:05:15,939 --> 00:05:17,415
<Default><b>I may be a princess</b></Default>

96
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:19,319
<Default><b>but more importantly</b></Default>

97
00:05:19,610 --> 00:05:20,819
<Default><b>[whines]</b></Default>

98
00:05:22,990 --> 00:05:24,079
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

99
00:05:24,160 --> 00:05:25,555
<Default><b>At the first
sign of trouble</b></Default>

100
00:05:25,579 --> 00:05:28,016
<Default><b>I'm sending you back
to town with a portal.</b></Default>

101
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:30,290
<Default><b>Yay! I feel fine now!</b></Default>

102
00:05:30,370 --> 00:05:31,459
<Default><b>Ah.</b></Default>

103
00:05:31,750 --> 00:05:34,420
<Default><b>Atla, can you keep
slowing down the curse?</b></Default>

104
00:05:34,709 --> 00:05:36,379
<Default><b>Yes. I'll do my best.</b></Default>

105
00:05:36,459 --> 00:05:38,300
<Default><b>If Atla's going</b></Default>

106
00:05:38,550 --> 00:05:40,235
<Default><b>I'm going too
no matter what.</b></Default>

107
00:05:40,259 --> 00:05:42,129
<Default><b>All right, all right</b></Default>

108
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:44,390
<Default><b>Everybody,
get ready to go.</b></Default>

109
00:05:45,889 --> 00:05:47,326
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
After that</b></Default>

110
00:05:47,350 --> 00:05:50,560
<Default><b>Filo raced to the village to
the east as fast as she could.</b></Default>

111
00:05:57,569 --> 00:05:59,149
<Default><b>[Filo panting]</b></Default>

112
00:05:59,279 --> 00:06:00,899
<Default><b>You did great, Filo.</b></Default>

113
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:03,569
<Default><b>I can fight too, Master.</b></Default>

114
00:06:03,660 --> 00:06:05,140
<Default><b>I just need a nap.</b></Default>

115
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:07,029
<Default><b>It'll only be a minute.</b></Default>

116
00:06:07,449 --> 00:06:08,199
<Default><b>- Ah!
- Savior!</b></Default>

117
00:06:08,290 --> 00:06:09,886
<Default><b>- The Shield Hero has come!
- Our hero!</b></Default>

118
00:06:09,910 --> 00:06:12,016
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Make sure
Filo gets some rest.</b></Default>

119
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:14,040
<Default><b>- [ATLA] Right.
- [MELTY] Right.</b></Default>

120
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,670
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

121
00:06:17,589 --> 00:06:19,750
<Default><b>She must be exhausted
right now.</b></Default>

122
00:06:19,959 --> 00:06:21,605
<Default><b>I might need
your help here.</b></Default>

123
00:06:21,629 --> 00:06:22,930
<Default><b>Very well!</b></Default>

124
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:25,009
<Default><b>Fast Aqua Heal!</b></Default>

125
00:06:26,009 --> 00:06:27,329
<Default><b>I'll help too!</b></Default>

126
00:06:27,389 --> 00:06:29,549
<Default><b>And go get something
for her to eat!</b></Default>

127
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:35,076
<Default><b>Thank goodness you've come
to help us, Shield Hero.</b></Default>

128
00:06:35,100 --> 00:06:38,020
<Default><b>Yet another dragon has found
its home near our village.</b></Default>

129
00:06:38,230 --> 00:06:39,586
<Default><b>Where did it go?</b></Default>

130
00:06:39,610 --> 00:06:40,755
<Default><b>[VILLAGER 08-A (M)]
Our best guess is</b></Default>

131
00:06:40,779 --> 00:06:42,625
<Default><b>that it went
to the Dragon's Den!</b></Default>

132
00:06:42,649 --> 00:06:43,929
<Default><b>Dragon's Den?</b></Default>

133
00:06:44,160 --> 00:06:46,846
<Default><b>There's a huge cave just beyond
that mountain over there</b></Default>

134
00:06:46,870 --> 00:06:49,630
<Default><b>the same one where that
horrible dragon once lived.</b></Default>

135
00:06:50,410 --> 00:06:51,636
<Default><b>But please be careful</b></Default>

136
00:06:51,660 --> 00:06:54,170
<Default><b>as our village won't survive
another plague.</b></Default>

137
00:06:54,290 --> 00:06:56,670
<Default><b>Save our village!
We beg of you!</b></Default>

138
00:06:58,709 --> 00:07:01,339
<Default><b>We don't have time
to waste on courtesies.</b></Default>

139
00:07:01,420 --> 00:07:02,605
<Default><b>We should get going.</b></Default>

140
00:07:02,629 --> 00:07:03,720
<Default><b>Agreed.</b></Default>

141
00:07:06,889 --> 00:07:09,180
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

142
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:26,425
<Default><b>[SADEENA] If we want to
put an end to this</b></Default>

143
00:07:26,449 --> 00:07:28,386
<Default><b>we'll need to first
weaken Gaelion</b></Default>

144
00:07:28,410 --> 00:07:31,490
<Default><b>and then make him spit up the
Emperor Dragon's Core, right?</b></Default>

145
00:07:31,699 --> 00:07:32,716
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Yes</b></Default>

146
00:07:32,740 --> 00:07:35,700
<Default><b>but what if it's taken over
Gaelion's whole body by now?</b></Default>

147
00:07:36,290 --> 00:07:39,170
<Default><b>[SADEENA] If so, then we'll
have a tough call to make.</b></Default>

148
00:07:41,050 --> 00:07:42,250
<Default><b>I see.</b></Default>

149
00:07:42,629 --> 00:07:44,759
<Default><b>[Monster 08-A roars]</b></Default>

150
00:07:47,050 --> 00:07:47,879
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

151
00:07:47,970 --> 00:07:49,180
<Default><b>[roars]</b></Default>

152
00:07:53,389 --> 00:07:56,100
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

153
00:07:57,350 --> 00:07:59,189
<Default><b>Dark Fire Palette!</b></Default>

154
00:08:06,149 --> 00:08:07,819
<Default><b>[roars]</b></Default>

155
00:08:09,610 --> 00:08:12,079
<Default><b>The hell?
Since when could you use magic?</b></Default>

156
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:14,699
<Default><b>I'm able to fight
if I have to, you know.</b></Default>

157
00:08:15,120 --> 00:08:17,160
<Default><b>Oh, my, you mean
you didn't know?</b></Default>

158
00:08:17,290 --> 00:08:20,170
<Default><b>Wyndia is able to use
the Way of the Dragon Vein.</b></Default>

159
00:08:20,250 --> 00:08:22,090
<Default><b>What kind of
magic is that?</b></Default>

160
00:08:22,209 --> 00:08:25,065
<Default><b>She can take power from the
Dragon Veins beneath the Earth</b></Default>

161
00:08:25,089 --> 00:08:26,609
<Default><b>to power her magic.</b></Default>

162
00:08:26,670 --> 00:08:28,065
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Once she masters it</b></Default>

163
00:08:28,089 --> 00:08:31,430
<Default><b>she'll be able to use both
Choral Magic and Jamming Magic.</b></Default>

164
00:08:31,930 --> 00:08:33,809
<Default><b>She can use
Choral Magic?</b></Default>

165
00:08:34,509 --> 00:08:36,429
<Default><b>Wyndia, you're
incredible.</b></Default>

166
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,809
<Default><b>My dad taught me
everything I know.</b></Default>

167
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:50,450
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

168
00:08:51,909 --> 00:08:53,096
<Default><b>[MELTY] You okay?</b></Default>

169
00:08:53,120 --> 00:08:54,556
<Default><b>[ATLA]
How do you feel, Filo?</b></Default>

170
00:08:54,580 --> 00:08:55,885
<Default><b>[FOHL]
You're in luck!</b></Default>

171
00:08:55,909 --> 00:08:57,989
<Default><b>I got a lot of fish
for you, Filo!</b></Default>

172
00:08:58,250 --> 00:08:59,419
<Default><b>Raphy.</b></Default>

173
00:09:00,419 --> 00:09:02,669
<Default><b>Thank you so
much everyone.</b></Default>

174
00:09:02,830 --> 00:09:05,500
<Default><b>- I'm feeling, ah..
- Filo!</b></Default>

175
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:08,129
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

176
00:09:14,850 --> 00:09:17,480
<Default><b>Filo, Hang in there
a little longer!</b></Default>

177
00:09:18,139 --> 00:09:19,615
<Default><b>[MELTY] Poor Filo.</b></Default>

178
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:21,190
<Default><b>It's gonna be okay!</b></Default>

179
00:09:23,730 --> 00:09:25,480
<Default><b>[screams]</b></Default>

180
00:09:28,190 --> 00:09:30,200
<Default><b>[fire crackling]</b></Default>

181
00:09:37,789 --> 00:09:40,469
<Default><b>[REN] So this is where it
became a dragon zombie?</b></Default>

182
00:09:41,539 --> 00:09:44,579
<Default><b>When I think about the people
who suffered because of that</b></Default>

183
00:09:44,710 --> 00:09:46,710
<Default><b>I feel as if I
can never atone.</b></Default>

184
00:09:47,419 --> 00:09:48,659
<Default><b>[Ren grunts]</b></Default>

185
00:09:53,509 --> 00:09:54,655
<Default><b>[Ren sighs]</b></Default>

186
00:09:54,679 --> 00:09:56,785
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] If a hero wants to
save the world</b></Default>

187
00:09:56,809 --> 00:09:57,946
<Default><b>he has to get stronger</b></Default>

188
00:09:57,970 --> 00:10:00,730
<Default><b>even if it means sacrificing
something dear to him.</b></Default>

189
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:03,119
<Default><b>Stand strong, Ren.</b></Default>

190
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,690
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

191
00:10:15,529 --> 00:10:17,529
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
This must be the spot.</b></Default>

192
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:20,230
<Default><b>Look over there.</b></Default>

193
00:10:22,620 --> 00:10:24,700
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
That's the Dragon's Den.</b></Default>

194
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:38,929
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Raphtalia</b></Default>

195
00:10:39,009 --> 00:10:40,365
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA] Yes.</b></Default>

196
00:10:40,389 --> 00:10:41,769
<Default><b>Drifa Light!</b></Default>

197
00:10:49,149 --> 00:10:51,360
<Default><b>Just how deep
do these caves go?</b></Default>

198
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:54,200
<Default><b>Do you really think
Gaelion is down here somewhere?</b></Default>

199
00:11:01,370 --> 00:11:02,726
<Default><b>[Wyndia scream]</b></Default>

200
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:03,885
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

201
00:11:03,909 --> 00:11:05,620
<Default><b>[RAPHTALIA]
Ren, Wyndia!</b></Default>

202
00:11:07,710 --> 00:11:09,840
<Default><b>[Ren grunts]</b></Default>

203
00:11:11,299 --> 00:11:13,049
<Default><b>Wyndia, Ren!</b></Default>

204
00:11:17,600 --> 00:11:19,040
<Default><b>[REN] We're fine.</b></Default>

205
00:11:21,389 --> 00:11:22,669
<Default><b>Are you okay?</b></Default>

206
00:11:23,269 --> 00:11:24,389
<Default><b>I am.</b></Default>

207
00:11:25,440 --> 00:11:26,840
<Default><b>That's a relief.</b></Default>

208
00:11:27,149 --> 00:11:29,019
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Air Strike Shield!</b></Default>

209
00:11:33,070 --> 00:11:34,916
<Default><b>Will you wait
outside for us?</b></Default>

210
00:11:34,940 --> 00:11:36,070
<Default><b>Mm-mmm.</b></Default>

211
00:11:36,490 --> 00:11:37,700
<Default><b>I'm coming!</b></Default>

212
00:11:38,409 --> 00:11:39,729
<Default><b>If you say so.</b></Default>

213
00:11:48,830 --> 00:11:51,066
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] What in the world
is this place?</b></Default>

214
00:11:51,090 --> 00:11:53,355
<Default><b>Even the light can't reach
all the way back there.</b></Default>

215
00:11:53,379 --> 00:11:55,139
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
Give me a second.</b></Default>

216
00:11:58,929 --> 00:12:01,049
<Default><b>Wyndia, what
are you doing?</b></Default>

217
00:12:03,769 --> 00:12:06,350
<Default><b>Dragon Vein</b></Default>

218
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,940
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

219
00:12:12,519 --> 00:12:15,279
<Default><b>Whoa!</b></Default>

220
00:12:18,450 --> 00:12:19,810
<Default><b>It's beautiful.</b></Default>

221
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:23,280
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Have you been here before?</b></Default>

222
00:12:23,580 --> 00:12:25,289
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
Yeah, long ago.</b></Default>

223
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,330
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

224
00:12:29,789 --> 00:12:31,169
<Default><b>Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

225
00:12:36,970 --> 00:12:39,340
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

226
00:12:39,429 --> 00:12:40,525
<Default><b>Gaelion, stop!</b></Default>

227
00:12:40,549 --> 00:12:43,929
<Default><b>Filo, no!</b></Default>

228
00:12:44,559 --> 00:12:46,600
<Default><b>[all screaming]</b></Default>

229
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:53,679
<Default><b>[MELTY] Filo!</b></Default>

230
00:12:53,940 --> 00:12:55,375
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
What happened?</b></Default>

231
00:12:55,399 --> 00:12:56,796
<Default><b>Filo went crazy!</b></Default>

232
00:12:56,820 --> 00:12:58,255
<Default><b>[MELTY]
No matter what we try</b></Default>

233
00:12:58,279 --> 00:13:00,676
<Default><b>she just won't listen to
anything we to tell her!</b></Default>

234
00:13:00,700 --> 00:13:01,780
<Default><b>[growls]</b></Default>

235
00:13:01,820 --> 00:13:03,580
<Default><b>What's gotten into her?</b></Default>

236
00:13:09,580 --> 00:13:10,820
<Default><b>Don't do it!</b></Default>

237
00:13:13,210 --> 00:13:14,549
<Default><b>Did it just...</b></Default>

238
00:13:15,460 --> 00:13:17,299
<Default><b>[growls]</b></Default>

239
00:13:17,379 --> 00:13:18,759
<Default><b>Filo, no!</b></Default>

240
00:13:20,549 --> 00:13:21,735
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
She's still there!</b></Default>

241
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:23,279
<Default><b>Filo's still alive!</b></Default>

242
00:13:23,639 --> 00:13:26,405
<Default><b>If we get the core back from
Gaelion then she'll be fine!</b></Default>

243
00:13:26,429 --> 00:13:27,655
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Don't let him absorb her!</b></Default>

244
00:13:27,679 --> 00:13:29,639
<Default><b>- Right!
- [grunts]</b></Default>

245
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:33,019
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

246
00:13:33,100 --> 00:13:34,730
<Default><b>Meteor Slash!</b></Default>

247
00:13:34,860 --> 00:13:36,700
<Default><b>[SADEENA]
Zweit Thunderbolt!</b></Default>

248
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:39,029
<Default><b>[crashes]</b></Default>

249
00:13:40,740 --> 00:13:42,779
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

250
00:13:45,120 --> 00:13:46,240
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

251
00:13:47,659 --> 00:13:49,789
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

252
00:13:51,580 --> 00:13:53,210
<Default><b>[all gasping]</b></Default>

253
00:13:55,789 --> 00:13:58,419
<Default><b>[growling]</b></Default>

254
00:14:00,509 --> 00:14:01,696
<Default><b>[all gasping]</b></Default>

255
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,389
<Default><b>That thing's gigantic.</b></Default>

256
00:14:06,350 --> 00:14:07,405
<Default><b>I'll stop it!</b></Default>

257
00:14:07,429 --> 00:14:08,970
<Default><b>Stardust Blade!</b></Default>

258
00:14:09,059 --> 00:14:10,889
<Default><b>Meteor Slash!</b></Default>

259
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:14,350
<Default><b>[grunts] It's tough!</b></Default>

260
00:14:16,149 --> 00:14:17,909
<Default><b>Lightning
Strike Harpoon!</b></Default>

261
00:14:19,490 --> 00:14:22,029
<Default><b>[zapping]</b></Default>

262
00:14:22,399 --> 00:14:24,200
<Default><b>It's tough indeed.</b></Default>

263
00:14:24,490 --> 00:14:26,426
<Default><b>Not even my strongest attack
works.</b></Default>

264
00:14:26,450 --> 00:14:28,610
<Default><b>I'll use magic to make you
stronger.</b></Default>

265
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:30,789
<Default><b>All Zweit Aura!</b></Default>

266
00:14:34,250 --> 00:14:35,919
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

267
00:14:36,629 --> 00:14:39,169
<Default><b>Light Stardust Blade!</b></Default>

268
00:14:42,509 --> 00:14:43,605
<Default><b>It worked!</b></Default>

269
00:14:43,629 --> 00:14:45,470
<Default><b>[roars]</b></Default>

270
00:14:45,549 --> 00:14:47,029
<Default><b>[ECLAIR]
Over here!</b></Default>

271
00:14:47,389 --> 00:14:48,600
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

272
00:14:50,519 --> 00:14:52,309
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

273
00:14:53,769 --> 00:14:55,980
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

274
00:14:57,769 --> 00:14:59,649
<Default><b>You better
give back Filo!</b></Default>

275
00:15:00,070 --> 00:15:02,440
<Default><b>Drifa Aqua Slash!</b></Default>

276
00:15:06,450 --> 00:15:08,409
<Default><b>[roars]</b></Default>

277
00:15:11,659 --> 00:15:13,159
<Default><b>They did it!</b></Default>

278
00:15:14,370 --> 00:15:15,690
<Default><b>[Wyndia gasps]</b></Default>

279
00:15:15,750 --> 00:15:17,919
<Default><b>[weak growl]</b></Default>

280
00:15:19,039 --> 00:15:21,025
<Default><b>It's working!
Now let's finish this!</b></Default>

281
00:15:21,049 --> 00:15:22,569
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
Wait don't!</b></Default>

282
00:15:22,919 --> 00:15:24,919
<Default><b>That's enough,
everybody!</b></Default>

283
00:15:25,129 --> 00:15:26,446
<Default><b>Please stop it.</b></Default>

284
00:15:26,470 --> 00:15:28,310
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
Stop all this, Dad!</b></Default>

285
00:15:28,639 --> 00:15:30,720
<Default><b>[voice echoes]
Dad! Dad! Dad!</b></Default>

286
00:15:37,309 --> 00:15:40,570
<Default><b>Please, Dad.
Please don't fight anymore.</b></Default>

287
00:15:42,360 --> 00:15:44,480
<Default><b>Wyndia, what are you
talking about?</b></Default>

288
00:15:46,029 --> 00:15:47,549
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
My dad is..</b></Default>

289
00:15:47,779 --> 00:15:50,779
<Default><b>My dad was the dragon
that lived in this area.</b></Default>

290
00:15:51,539 --> 00:15:54,250
<Default><b>[Wyndia crying]</b></Default>

291
00:16:01,500 --> 00:16:03,879
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

292
00:16:05,419 --> 00:16:08,220
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
No! Let go of me!</b></Default>

293
00:16:08,299 --> 00:16:10,009
<Default><b>Dad, help!</b></Default>

294
00:16:11,179 --> 00:16:13,429
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
Dad, help me!</b></Default>

295
00:16:17,809 --> 00:16:19,129
<Default><b>Does that mean</b></Default>

296
00:16:19,440 --> 00:16:20,760
<Default><b>I was the one.</b></Default>

297
00:16:21,570 --> 00:16:22,956
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
So that's it.</b></Default>

298
00:16:22,980 --> 00:16:25,690
<Default><b>He became a dragon zombie
to try and protect her.</b></Default>

299
00:16:26,860 --> 00:16:28,490
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

300
00:16:33,330 --> 00:16:35,290
<Default><b>[WYNDIA]
Ever since my dad died</b></Default>

301
00:16:35,830 --> 00:16:38,039
<Default><b>I hated them
with all my heart.</b></Default>

302
00:16:38,120 --> 00:16:40,556
<Default><b>I told myself I couldn't
forgive the heroes</b></Default>

303
00:16:40,580 --> 00:16:42,260
<Default><b>for destroying my life.</b></Default>

304
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:44,880
<Default><b>However</b></Default>

305
00:16:44,919 --> 00:16:47,879
<Default><b>the Shield Hero was kind to me
when no one else was!</b></Default>

306
00:16:48,009 --> 00:16:49,566
<Default><b>He's not like everyone else
here</b></Default>

307
00:16:49,590 --> 00:16:51,429
<Default><b>who mistreats
Demi-humans!</b></Default>

308
00:16:51,720 --> 00:16:53,696
<Default><b>Or the villagers who
stole your treasure</b></Default>

309
00:16:53,720 --> 00:16:56,679
<Default><b>and turned your body
into a spectacle for others!</b></Default>

310
00:16:57,769 --> 00:17:01,269
<Default><b>Please, give little Gaelion
back his body.</b></Default>

311
00:17:01,519 --> 00:17:02,586
<Default><b>You hear that?</b></Default>

312
00:17:02,610 --> 00:17:04,666
<Default><b>He's even got the same name
as you.</b></Default>

313
00:17:04,690 --> 00:17:06,490
<Default><b>And he's still
alive, Dad.</b></Default>

314
00:17:07,990 --> 00:17:09,200
<Default><b>[sobs]</b></Default>

315
00:17:09,279 --> 00:17:11,045
<Default><b>You can't stay
here anymore!</b></Default>

316
00:17:11,069 --> 00:17:13,109
<Default><b>Not when you're acting
like this!</b></Default>

317
00:17:17,660 --> 00:17:18,789
<Default><b>[growls]</b></Default>

318
00:17:19,250 --> 00:17:21,579
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

319
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:24,799
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

320
00:17:29,049 --> 00:17:30,720
<Default><b>[Ren groans]</b></Default>

321
00:17:32,130 --> 00:17:33,299
<Default><b>[groans]</b></Default>

322
00:17:33,470 --> 00:17:34,809
<Default><b>No, Ren!</b></Default>

323
00:17:35,259 --> 00:17:36,446
<Default><b>Wyndia, are you hurt?</b></Default>

324
00:17:36,470 --> 00:17:37,559
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

325
00:17:37,890 --> 00:17:39,035
<Default><b>Are you okay?</b></Default>

326
00:17:39,059 --> 00:17:41,349
<Default><b>I'm fine</b></Default>

327
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:43,000
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Drifa Heal!</b></Default>

328
00:17:44,900 --> 00:17:46,519
<Default><b>Ren, can you fight?</b></Default>

329
00:17:46,819 --> 00:17:48,319
<Default><b>Yeah, just barely.</b></Default>

330
00:17:53,660 --> 00:17:56,490
<Default><b>Who're you?
You're nothing like my dad!</b></Default>

331
00:17:56,829 --> 00:17:59,410
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

332
00:18:01,619 --> 00:18:03,210
<Default><b>Wyndia, get back!</b></Default>

333
00:18:12,170 --> 00:18:14,680
<Default><b>[EMPEROR DRAGON]
I am the Emperor Dragon</b></Default>

334
00:18:15,509 --> 00:18:19,059
<Default><b>ruler of all monsters
beneath the stars!</b></Default>

335
00:18:20,180 --> 00:18:21,640
<Default><b>Him again?</b></Default>

336
00:18:22,140 --> 00:18:23,780
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
So that's it.</b></Default>

337
00:18:23,809 --> 00:18:26,706
<Default><b>Combining the cores of the
zombie dragon from this world</b></Default>

338
00:18:26,730 --> 00:18:28,585
<Default><b>and the Emperor Dragon
from Kizuna's</b></Default>

339
00:18:28,609 --> 00:18:30,729
<Default><b>caused their souls
to mix into one!</b></Default>

340
00:18:31,859 --> 00:18:33,585
<Default><b>[EMPEROR DRAGON]
My festered rage</b></Default>

341
00:18:33,609 --> 00:18:35,990
<Default><b>craves to take control
of this world</b></Default>

342
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:38,079
<Default><b>from you
pathetic humans!</b></Default>

343
00:18:38,410 --> 00:18:40,539
<Default><b>And once I do.</b></Default>

344
00:18:40,619 --> 00:18:43,920
<Default><b>I'll kill the Hunting Hero
and her comrades</b></Default>

345
00:18:44,000 --> 00:18:46,579
<Default><b>who crushed
my burning ambitions.</b></Default>

346
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:50,100
<Default><b>[ATLA]
Master Naofumi!</b></Default>

347
00:18:50,170 --> 00:18:52,235
<Default><b>An incredible amount
of power is flowing</b></Default>

348
00:18:52,259 --> 00:18:54,619
<Default><b>from your shield
into the Emperor Dragon.</b></Default>

349
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:58,059
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] It's fine.
Stand back, Atla.</b></Default>

350
00:18:58,140 --> 00:18:59,309
<Default><b>But you?</b></Default>

351
00:19:02,309 --> 00:19:03,349
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

352
00:19:03,430 --> 00:19:06,690
<Default><b>Just what did
you do with</b></Default>

353
00:19:08,109 --> 00:19:10,456
<Default><b>[EMPEROR DRAGON] I take it
you're referring to the monster</b></Default>

354
00:19:10,480 --> 00:19:13,029
<Default><b>they call a Filolial
in this world?</b></Default>

355
00:19:18,279 --> 00:19:19,410
<Default><b>Filo, no!</b></Default>

356
00:19:19,490 --> 00:19:21,210
<Default><b>- [Sadeena gasps.
- Filo!</b></Default>

357
00:19:24,289 --> 00:19:26,265
<Default><b>[EMPEROR DRAGON] I'm sure
she's more than happy</b></Default>

358
00:19:26,289 --> 00:19:28,289
<Default><b>to serve as
part of my flesh!</b></Default>

359
00:19:31,670 --> 00:19:32,960
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

360
00:19:33,049 --> 00:19:34,396
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Zweit Aura!</b></Default>

361
00:19:34,420 --> 00:19:35,970
<Default><b>Raphtalia!</b></Default>

362
00:19:36,589 --> 00:19:37,589
<Default><b>On it!</b></Default>

363
00:19:38,220 --> 00:19:39,720
<Default><b>Air Strike Shield!</b></Default>

364
00:19:41,099 --> 00:19:43,430
<Default><b>Light Stardust Blade!</b></Default>

365
00:19:44,680 --> 00:19:46,140
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

366
00:19:47,349 --> 00:19:48,900
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

367
00:19:48,980 --> 00:19:50,400
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

368
00:19:56,029 --> 00:19:57,779
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

369
00:20:00,279 --> 00:20:02,200
<Default><b>Drifa Aqua Slash!</b></Default>

370
00:20:06,460 --> 00:20:07,595
<Default><b>This isn't working.</b></Default>

371
00:20:07,619 --> 00:20:09,686
<Default><b>My attacks aren't
even affecting him!</b></Default>

372
00:20:09,710 --> 00:20:12,049
<Default><b>[MELTY]
He's nullifying my magic, too!</b></Default>

373
00:20:12,670 --> 00:20:14,420
<Default><b>There is still one way.</b></Default>

374
00:20:15,210 --> 00:20:17,606
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] I think he's getting
his massive defense stats</b></Default>

375
00:20:17,630 --> 00:20:18,990
<Default><b>from my shield.</b></Default>

376
00:20:20,140 --> 00:20:22,349
<Default><b>Which means</b></Default>

377
00:20:22,430 --> 00:20:24,575
<Default><b>a power-up attempt
on the Wrath Shield</b></Default>

378
00:20:24,599 --> 00:20:26,230
<Default><b>it should weaken him.</b></Default>

379
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:30,269
<Default><b>But still, that'll just end up
weakening you too, won't it?</b></Default>

380
00:20:30,519 --> 00:20:32,166
<Default><b>There's no
time for caution!</b></Default>

381
00:20:32,190 --> 00:20:33,626
<Default><b>Filo won't
last until then...</b></Default>

382
00:20:33,650 --> 00:20:35,416
<Default><b>[EMPEROR DRAGON]
You really think I'll stand by</b></Default>

383
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:37,490
<Default><b>and let you do
such a thing?</b></Default>

384
00:20:38,609 --> 00:20:39,990
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

385
00:20:44,700 --> 00:20:46,176
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
He took it over?</b></Default>

386
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:48,170
<Default><b>[beeping]</b></Default>

387
00:20:54,130 --> 00:20:56,460
<Default><b>[fire roaring]</b></Default>

388
00:20:58,180 --> 00:20:59,509
<Default><b>Get back!</b></Default>

389
00:21:01,589 --> 00:21:03,349
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

390
00:21:05,849 --> 00:21:07,930
<Default><b>[all screaming]</b></Default>

391
00:21:12,349 --> 00:21:14,150
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

392
00:21:14,230 --> 00:21:15,569
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

393
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:26,539
<Default><b>Raphtalia!</b></Default>

394
00:21:31,619 --> 00:21:34,589
<Default><b>[WYNDIA] Please, Dad!
Stop this and come back!</b></Default>

395
00:21:38,970 --> 00:21:40,759
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

396
00:21:42,140 --> 00:21:43,580
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI]
Damn it!</b></Default>

397
00:21:46,180 --> 00:21:47,866
<Default><b>[NAOFUMI] Meteor Shield!
Air Strike Shield!</b></Default>

398
00:21:47,890 --> 00:21:49,706
<Default><b>Second Shield!
Dritte Shield!</b></Default>

399
00:21:49,730 --> 00:21:51,099
<Default><b>E Float Shield!</b></Default>

400
00:21:51,599 --> 00:21:54,190
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

401
00:21:54,440 --> 00:21:56,569
<Default><b>[explosion]</b></Default>

402
00:21:58,990 --> 00:22:01,990
<Default><b>[screaming]</b></Default>

